data.description: Newer home located in the Shadow Ridge Subdivision on the West side of Paragould. All brick with 4 spacious bedrooms and 2.5 baths. Soaring vaulted ceilings in the living space that is open into the kitchen and dining area. Lots of cabinetry, island with breakfast bar, granite countertops, white kitchen with timeless subway tile backsplash. LVP flooring throughout. White wash/Stone gas log fireplace  that is definitely a statement piece! Primary suite has a massive closet, tile shower and soaker tub with a walk through laundry room! Foyer has the perfect spot for storage! Screened in back porch with privacy fenced in backyard.
